{
  "stem": "5559.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, I-- my mother slept separate in a children bed, you know-- in a baby crib.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had to hang over her feet to open the baby crib, and there was a little box so she can hold her legs on the box.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how she slept, in a baby crib.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And me and my father slept what they called in a regular steel bed, but no mattress, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know if you ever saw these.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These have these, oh God, springs, but not mattress.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, these steel beds, they have springs?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how you sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sure, you wake up, you have wounds, but you sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one night, in the morning, we wake up, and my mother start crying, pulling her hair, oy gevalt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Dad is-- my father is dead, OK?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was a big winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was two ways.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Either let-- also let him up on the cemetery and will be buried in the mass grave, like they blow up with dynamite, eh?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or do something about, and do just that what you could do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Do it on your-- no funeral, naturally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no funeral director, or funeral, or a casket, or so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Forget about that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my mother had a [NON-ENGLISH] which was a very expensive fur coat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, here it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want to bury my husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they organize that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first, they-- they brought-- I call it a troika-- one of these flat, little carriage with the Russian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see them sometime in the movie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are flat, and a big horse with a thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like If you watched the movie, you saw these flat, little things.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
